<section class="cta">
  <div class="card viewer">
    <div class="step mono">// for viewers</div>
    <h3>Watch privately.</h3>
    <p>Install the browser extension to swap out undefended players for Dodge, apply ready-made defenses, and verify them.</p>
    <a href="/install">Install →</a>
  </div>
  <div class="card builder">
    <div class="step mono">// for builders</div>
    <h3>Defend your video catalog.</h3>
    <p>Use the dash.js module, generate defenses using our tools or your own tools that follow the extended manifest spec.</p>
    <a href="/tools">Tools and spec →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .card {
    padding: 32px 36px;
  }
  .card + .card {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .step {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  p {
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--bg);
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  a:hover {
    background: var(--accent);
  }
  .builder a {
    background: var(--panel);
    color: var(--ink);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .builder a:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .cta {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .card + .card {
      border-left: 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
  }
</style>
